-- Glencore Purchase of Ukraine’s Kolos Is Cleared, Izvestia Says
-- B y   K a t e r y n a   C h o u r s i n a
-- 2012-02-13T09:05:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-13/glencore-purchase-of-ukraine-s-kolos-is-cleared-izvestia-says.html
Ukraine’s antitrust committee gave
the go-ahead for Swiss company Glencore International Plc to
acquire more than 50 percent of CHAO Kolos, an oilseed crusher
and fats producer,  Ekonomicheskie Izvestia  newspaper reported,
without citing anyone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kateryna Choursina in Kiev at 
